{"tid":1843424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺世界第一","createTime":"2020-01-26T07:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T08:20:56.000Z","uid":48452,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c6aa7597cd906418dc820fe9d61a966ad8dee46e","tid":1843424,"uid":48452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"今次事件睇得出粉嶺人嘅團結<br />\n好多高汁粉嶺人都全力守護自己地頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n粉嶺無得頂<br />\n居然有啲垃圾話粉嶺遠所以適合設立隔離區<br />\n粉嶺交通媲美九龍同港島  繁華程度絕對比得上市區<br />\n返大陸又方便<br />\n食嘢又平靚正 郊遊地點夠多 <br />\n有個大高爾夫球可以拆嚟起其他嘢<br />\n去林奠屋企找麻煩又最方便<br />\n全香港最出色嘅區就係粉嶺 <br />\n你哋班九龍港島人全部都弱雞<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fbfad40c9c13abff360a9c81afb08a6f71dc82","tid":1843424,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"快d去暉明樓下啦 開始多人"},{"pid":"33f56109ce879f4d2d203e141267766b24a1dc10","tid":1843424,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"9faffe443ca5e3f5562e6a3fd636c872d14ac01e","tid":1843424,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dprL7aq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdprL7aq.jpg&h=cfd5c185&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67b5e23c2198eaa469616ac2ab09345dc45f50af","tid":1843424,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港人自救</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b9c3e79dd1855be2967ed90318ea25ad0d4a9bfe","tid":1843424,"uid":281141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"粉嶺人自救！"}]}